text: We loved our stay at the Hyde Park Bungalow!  It is in a really great location and our family took walks around the beautiful neighborhood every evening.  A couple evenings we walked to a local spot for dinner.  The kitchen was well stocked and had everything we needed.  We really hope to stay at Ananda and Dunstan's place again because it was just lovely!
title: Hyde Park Bungalow close to UT & DT
